    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rogue Blight试玩版让你探索第一张地图“威伍德森林”，感受前方旅程的精彩片段。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个充满怪物、动作紧凑、受魂系列启发的2D rogue-lite游戏中，穿越被疫病侵袭的世界，奋勇战斗。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对各种强大的敌人和首领。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用类似魂系列的战斗风格进行战斗。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在无限的New Game+故事模式中迎接不断升级的挑战。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336830/extras/6d01070be52ce801d4d03a2b13a53cfb.poster.avif?t=1763149337\" width=1170 height=682 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336830/extras/6d01070be52ce801d4d03a2b13a53cfb.webm?t=1763149337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >角色进阶</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有武器为单手武器，可将剑、匕首、法杖或盾牌装备在任意手上，打造独特的构筑。（盾牌仅限左手装备）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >试玩版中有超过20种武器，每种武器都有独特技能。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对任何敌人（包括首领）施加状态效果，例如流血、中毒、燃烧、冻结、触电、窒息、粉碎、生命爆发、黑暗或光明攻击。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现大量祝福，这些独特物品可改变角色构筑。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提升角色等级，解锁种类丰富的武器、装备和祝福。试玩版等级上限为25。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >永久提升角色能力，并在未来的尝试中解锁更多选项。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336830/extras/db5f56942b45ab11475b1fa5e7db0d8b.poster.avif?t=1763149337\" width=1170 height=682 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336830/extras/db5f56942b45ab11475b1fa5e7db0d8b.webm?t=1763149337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >地图进程</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索3张*随机生成地图中的1张，每张地图都有独特的敌人、背景和随机事件。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >找到提供独特奖励的随机事件。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找装满祝福的宝箱。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >光顾商店，获取武器、装备和祝福。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过祈祷雕像来提升你的生命值、法力值或耐力值。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用铁匠将多余的装备熔炼，升级你的装备。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336830/extras/5d73470e3c888061f4bbd0395c3c9c3a.poster.avif?t=1763149337\" width=1170 height=682 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336830/extras/5d73470e3c888061f4bbd0395c3c9c3a.webm?t=1763149337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
